'''ISO 3166-2:BH''' is an [[ISO]] standard which defines [[geocode]]s.  It is the subset of [[ISO 3166-2]] that applies to [[Bahrain]].  Each two-part code consists of the [[ISO 3166-1]] code for Bahrain ('''BH''') and a two-digit number.

